Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.54,0:03:58.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个势力绑架了玛斯德·拉弗玛迪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.22,0:04:00.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然只是我的推测而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.19,0:04:03.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但吠陀也暗示了相同的意见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.61,0:04:05.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推测的根据呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.27,0:04:12.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接收天线的建设现场  受到了远方的导弹攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.38,0:04:16.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就火力方面而言  使用了MS的可能性很高
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.29,0:04:19.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能运用MS的组织…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.85,0:04:22.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.76,0:04:23.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.18,0:04:26.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以让刹那去调查了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.99,0:04:29.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个国家  我们太过于显眼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.70,0:04:35.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据洛克昂的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.60,0:04:38.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎应该是这一带发射的导弹…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.72,0:04:44.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,残留反应  这里确实有MS出现过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.35,0:04:46.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但会是哪里来的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.49,0:04:58.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联合…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.86,0:05:00.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和回收了的登陆舱一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.71,0:05:03.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种反应  果然错不了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.71,0:05:06.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们也在对这里进行搜查
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.24,0:05:09.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PMC Trust那边的意见呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.52,0:05:13.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫拉里亚纷争地区发现的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.77,0:05:15.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.99,0:05:17.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那边偷听可不好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.03,0:05:19.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.38,0:05:21.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快出来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.57,0:05:28.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是附近的孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.23,0:05:29.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.14,0:05:34.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我…听说这附近发生了战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.73,0:05:35.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.59,0:05:36.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.07,0:05:40.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不是不理解你到了对这些事感兴趣的年龄了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.13,0:05:45.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这附近仍然很危险  你最好快点离开
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.44,0:05:47.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  马上就走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.60,0:05:48.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.02,0:05:54.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.24,0:05:58.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么看待这个国家的内乱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.11,0:05:59.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.23,0:06:01.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格拉哈姆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.76,0:06:04.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎么看待这个国家的内乱的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.39,0:06:07.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.65,0:06:09.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法作出客观的判断吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.16,0:06:12.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  你支持哪方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.31,0:06:14.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…都不支持
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.37,0:06:17.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉两边都有着自己的正义
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.49,0:06:21.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是因为这次战斗  有人死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.41,0:06:24.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了很多人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.45,0:06:26.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有同感
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.43,0:06:29.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为军人的你也是这么想的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.56,0:06:32.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来到这个国家的我们很碍事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.87,0:06:36.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为  如果来了很多的军人的话  受害也会增加
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.13,0:06:39.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是也在战斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.14,0:06:43.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后面藏着的是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.13,0:06:49.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怕的表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.86,0:07:01.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,片桐  昨天从这里攻击接收天线的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.48,0:07:04.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是AEU最新锐的Enact吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.78,0:07:05.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然说些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.10,0:07:10.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那部机体似乎是从莫拉里亚的PMC抢的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.26,0:07:12.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.99,0:07:18.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格拉哈姆  为什么说这些
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.59,0:07:20.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.53,0:07:22.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多嘴也没什么借口的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.76,0:07:30.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PMC的Enact…难道是！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.06,0:07:42.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙…那个男人…和这次内乱有关
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.10,0:07:46.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.37,0:07:52.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何…为何到现在还…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.22,0:08:04.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是恐怖袭击吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.28,0:08:06.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说这附近改革派很多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.73,0:08:08.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用MS应对没什么效果
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.19,0:08:12.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能要求派遣对人镇压用自动机器人了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.62,0:08:13.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用没用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.02,0:08:16.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是专为Gundam派来的部队
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.74,0:08:20.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高层不可能派更多的部队来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.17,0:08:21.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是会精打细算啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.17,0:08:32.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受神的惩罚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.15,0:08:36.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛…玛丽娜殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.78,0:08:39.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请赐予神的嘱佑…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.53,0:08:49.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是太没用了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.98,0:08:56.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.45,0:08:59.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.71,0:09:00.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.65,0:09:02.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改革派的爪牙！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.42,0:09:19.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.52,0:09:23.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.24,0:09:30.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我们要如此相互憎恨呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.12,0:09:34.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.86,0:09:36.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,POINT F3987？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.17,0:09:38.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.61,0:09:39.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可能没有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.29,0:09:41.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.74,0:09:44.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总比没有强…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.24,0:09:46.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解了  刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.28,0:09:49.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能带红龙一起去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.67,0:09:53.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对救出重要人物会有帮助哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.49,0:09:59.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN系统保险解除
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.84,0:10:02.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优先权转至刹那·F·清英
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.82,0:10:05.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外部迷彩解冻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.95,0:10:08.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持散布GN粒子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.37,0:10:09.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入登机模式
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.89,0:10:22.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia  开始执行任务
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.95,0:10:35.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备好了吗  红龙先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.48,0:10:36.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.81,0:10:37.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.24,0:10:40.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dynames  前往目标地点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.00,0:10:46.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.07,0:10:50.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.26,0:10:54.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个老头别说吃饭了  连水都不喝一滴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.80,0:10:56.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管他别管他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.35,0:10:58.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是不想接受敌人的施舍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.03,0:11:03.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  这个国家的家伙都很顽固啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.18,0:11:10.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial什么的一来  全都搞得乱糟糟的了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.64,0:11:14.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长  有朝这里接近的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.20,0:11:16.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联合的侦查吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.76,0:11:17.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.16,0:11:21.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那白色的MS
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.01,0:11:23.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Gundam吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.25,0:11:35.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia  到达目标地点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.17,0:11:41.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.25,0:11:53.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.07,0:11:57.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam由我来应付
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.09,0:11:59.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带上老头撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.93,0:12:00.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.27,0:12:04.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架Enact
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.53,0:12:06.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.18,0:12:10.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  驾驶员果然是那个克鲁吉斯的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.13,0:12:14.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么知道这个隐蔽地点的话一点都不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.85,0:12:24.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到啊  那个时候的小鬼会坐上了Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.96,0:12:27.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的战斗还没结束吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.34,0:12:29.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.41,0:12:31.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克鲁吉斯已经灭亡了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.13,0:12:36.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.39,0:12:46.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.80,0:12:49.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的神到底在什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.16,0:12:52.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.31,0:12:54.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没必要回答你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.13,0:13:08.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太浪费了  那台机体让给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.79,0:13:10.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？  Gundam！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.42,0:13:12.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.49,0:13:18.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真干得出来啊  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.42,0:13:21.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍然在预料之中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.45,0:13:27.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未必吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.17,0:13:33.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.61,0:13:36.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.88,0:13:41.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长  我们遭到敌人袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.69,0:13:44.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切  没反应
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.90,0:13:45.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.84,0:13:48.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.65,0:13:56.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.98,0:14:02.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.41,0:14:05.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那个人交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.55,0:14:18.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身手看来还在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.65,0:14:21.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.72,0:14:23.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.59,0:14:25.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.69,0:14:30.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对阿扎提斯坦的内战进行武力干涉的私立武装组织
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.63,0:14:34.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  就是你们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.04,0:14:50.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请坐上来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.35,0:14:51.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.83,0:15:02.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后的任务  确实已经收到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.64,0:15:03.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.46,0:15:07.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么作战啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.51,0:15:09.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的下达了那样的指示吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.36,0:15:11.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有一步错了  Exia就…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.35,0:15:14.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是最切实的办法哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.59,0:15:15.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.64,0:15:18.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我赞成皇小姐的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.32,0:15:18.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.59,0:15:22.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有让世界见识的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.94,0:15:25.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being的理念
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.30,0:15:31.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽娜殿下  Celestial Being发来了消息
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.50,0:15:33.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being发来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.54,0:15:36.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「已救出玛斯德·拉弗玛迪  正在前来」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.92,0:15:41.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「并希望公主立刻召开停战会议  以上」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.63,0:15:47.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  马上去做会谈的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.53,0:15:48.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.74,0:15:52.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽娜殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.17,0:15:56.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实我不赞同他们的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.19,0:15:59.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有可能是陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.00,0:16:02.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  即使如此也很想相信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.89,0:16:05.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很想相信他们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.34,0:16:15.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being正在前往王宫  是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.27,0:16:17.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还带着人质
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.09,0:16:20.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真是这样的话可是最好的机会啊  中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.96,0:16:25.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拭目以待吧  Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.91,0:16:29.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是阿扎提斯坦的王宫前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.20,0:16:35.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说玛斯德·拉弗玛迪已被救出并正在前往王宫的市民们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.86,0:16:38.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纷纷聚集到了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.96,0:16:40.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是未经证实的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.52,0:16:45.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有消息说救出拉弗玛迪的是Celestial Being
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.65,0:16:48.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  Gundam会在这里出现吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.06,0:16:53.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎样  作为改革派的象征——玛丽娜·伊斯迈尔公主
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.33,0:16:57.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能实现和保守派的宗教领导人的双边会谈的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.91,0:17:02.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿扎提斯坦的内乱很有可能将会终结
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.40,0:17:06.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.92,0:17:12.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把沙慈放开啊  妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.22,0:17:17.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.47,0:17:19.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.39,0:17:20.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.02,0:17:22.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.85,0:17:31.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.26,0:17:34.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam从高空降落下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.73,0:17:36.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害  真的来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.68,0:17:38.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.29,0:17:46.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚  Gundam在王宫前缓缓着陆了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.95,0:17:50.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然解除了武装？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.83,0:17:53.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真蠢啊  居然毫无武装的来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.04,0:17:55.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要攻击Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.75,0:17:56.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.93,0:17:58.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.85,0:18:01.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚出这片契约之地！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.10,0:18:05.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是枪击  数名市民正在向Gundam射击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.20,0:18:06.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.44,0:18:08.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊  沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.18,0:18:13.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam动起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.00,0:18:16.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正朝着王宫慢慢前进
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.68,0:18:21.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立即释放挟持的人质
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.10,0:18:25.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复  立即释放挟持的人质
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.88,0:18:26.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.65,0:18:27.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.78,0:18:35.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.98,0:18:41.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.04,0:18:42.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽娜殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.54,0:18:50.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.40,0:19:03.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次一定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.11,0:19:11.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.20,0:19:40.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请前往王宫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.28,0:19:44.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  真不算是很舒适的一趟旅程呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.57,0:19:46.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.00,0:19:49.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该向你道谢才是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.54,0:19:51.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请快点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.46,0:19:58.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是玛斯德·拉弗玛迪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.06,0:20:03.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being保护玛斯德·拉弗玛迪并移送到了王宫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.55,0:20:09.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.32,0:20:10.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.69,0:20:11.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那·F·清英
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.18,0:20:17.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  真的是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.55,0:20:20.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽娜·伊斯迈尔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.46,0:20:22.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来全看你的了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.50,0:20:25.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是否还会再来也是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.15,0:20:28.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.86,0:20:33.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗吧  为了你所信奉的神
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.92,0:20:35.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.95,0:20:44.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉  追吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.31,0:20:45.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的话Gundam还…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.85,0:20:46.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能才怪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.51,0:20:52.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样做的话  我们将会成为世界的靶子的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.33,0:20:59.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是吓出了一身冷汗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.25,0:21:02.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  大小姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.06,0:21:05.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样这个问题就能解决了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.31,0:21:07.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.36,0:21:13.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  能为阻止人们的纷争走出第一步
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.36,0:21:16.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走出第一步
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.09,0:21:32.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛斯德·拉弗玛迪宣布绑架他的武装集团是佣兵部队
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.15,0:21:35.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及此次内乱是精心筹划的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.55,0:21:41.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主谋似乎是企图阻止阿扎提斯坦的近代化变革的势力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.05,0:21:44.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但没有发表任何犯罪声明
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.70,0:21:50.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后  玛丽娜·伊斯迈尔及玛斯德·拉弗玛迪发布共同声明
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.81,0:21:55.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼吁国民停止内战及恐怖袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.97,0:22:00.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  阿扎提斯坦的内乱至今仍在继续
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.93,0:23:38.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由三个国家群的共同军事演习引起的纷争
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.61,0:23:41.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝着奔向险境的Meister心中袭来的东西会是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.71,0:23:44.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  「决意的早晨」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.12,0:23:47.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是Gundam的话…
